01:49:49,900 --> 01:49:52,120
我会留在圣巴巴拉
I'll stay in Santa Barbara.

1488
01:49:52,600 --> 01:49:55,420
两年之后我会嫁给戴夫
In just two years I will marry Dave.

1489
01:49:56,220 --> 01:50:00,000
我结婚后的一个月 卡洛塔会死去
A month after I get married Carlotta will die.

1490
01:50:02,660 --> 01:50:05,810
一个星期后 马克思也会死去
A week later... Max will die too.

1491
01:50:08,370 --> 01:50:10,180
我会从车库里工作
I will work out of my garage.

1492
01:50:10,220 --> 01:50:12,300
然后在当地艺廊里展出
and show in local galleries.

1493
01:50:13,620 --> 01:50:16,920
我会不顾医生的建议去怀孕
Against my doctor's advice, I will get pregnant..

1494
01:50:17,580 --> 01:50:21,340
