by the time I'm 34 I'll have two boys...

1495
01:50:25,500 --> 01:50:27,710
我会和多萝西娅一起再生活一年
I'll live with Dorothea for another year.

1496
01:50:30,240 --> 01:50:32,310
然后我会开一家陶器店
And then I'll open a pottery store.

1497
01:50:32,380 --> 01:50:34,760
