In Sedona, Arizona.

1498
01:50:37,710 --> 01:50:40,610
我会和一个叫劳丽的原创歌手结婚
I will marry Laurie a singer-songwriter...

1499
01:50:40,870 --> 01:50:44,730
我们会在一年后离婚 接着我会遇见桑迪
We'll get divorced a year...Then I'll meet Sandy.

1500
01:50:45,600 --> 01:50:47,970
并且继续做我的陶器
And continue to do my pottery.

1501
01:50:50,400 --> 01:50:53,420
我妈妈会在1983年遇见吉姆
My mom will meet Jim in 1983...

1502
01:50:54,540 --> 01:50:57,170
他们会一直是夫妻 直到她去世 
they'll stay a couple until she dies.

1503
01:50:57,880 --> 01:50:59,630
每年她生日的时候
On her birthday each year,

1504
01:50:59,920 --> 01:51:02,560
